Text.SourceString: Music makes everything better, don't you think?
Text.LocalizedString: Music makes everything better, don't you think?

Text.SourceString: I wonder what life’s gonna be like when I’m an adult.
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder what life’s gonna be like when I’m an adult.

Text.SourceString: Weekends are way too short. Two days isn't enough to recover.
Text.LocalizedString: Weekends are way too short. Two days isn't enough to recover.

Text.SourceString: I swear I need more sleep than most people.
Text.LocalizedString: I swear I need more sleep than most people.

Text.SourceString: I can't tell if I'm more tired or more hungry. Probably both.
Text.LocalizedString: I can't tell if I'm more tired or more hungry. Probably both.

Text.SourceString: Hey, {ParentLabel}, ever think I could go pro in gaming? That’d be living the dream, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, {ParentLabel}, ever think I could go pro in gaming? That’d be living the dream, right?

Text.SourceString: Algebra? Seriously? When am I ever gonna use this stuff?
Text.LocalizedString: Algebra? Seriously? When am I ever gonna use this stuff?

Text.SourceString: Why does time drag in school but fly when I'm having fun?
Text.LocalizedString: Why does time drag in school but fly when I'm having fun?

Text.SourceString: People say high school is the best time of your life... I don’t see it.
Text.LocalizedString: People say high school is the best time of your life... I don’t see it.

Text.SourceString: What should I have for lunch? Decisions, decisions...
Text.LocalizedString: What should I have for lunch? Decisions, decisions...

Text.SourceString: What should I have for lunch? Decisions, decisions...
Text.LocalizedString: What should I have for lunch? Decisions, decisions...

Text.SourceString: I'm so hungry. Got any good snacks, {ParentLabel}?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm so hungry. Got any good snacks, {ParentLabel}?

Text.SourceString: Stayed up way too late binge-watching last night. No regrets! Just, uh, don’t mention it to {SpouseLabel}, okay?
Text.LocalizedString: Stayed up way too late binge-watching last night. No regrets! Just, uh, don’t mention it to {SpouseLabel}, okay?

Text.SourceString: I still have no clue what I want to do when I grow up... Does anyone, really?
Text.LocalizedString: I still have no clue what I want to do when I grow up... Does anyone, really?

Text.SourceString: Maybe I’ll travel the world when I’m older. Think of all the amazing places I could see. You cool with that, {ParentLabel}?
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I’ll travel the world when I’m older. Think of all the amazing places I could see. You cool with that, {ParentLabel}?

Text.SourceString: I kinda want to do something creative. Like maybe design video games.
Text.LocalizedString: I kinda want to do something creative. Like maybe design video games.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I think being a vet would be awesome. I’d get to hang out with animals all day!
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I think being a vet would be awesome. I’d get to hang out with animals all day!

Text.SourceString: Spring just feels so fresh, like a reset for everything!
Text.LocalizedString: Spring just feels so fresh, like a reset for everything!

Text.SourceString: No more freezing mornings! Finally.
Text.LocalizedString: No more freezing mornings! Finally.

Text.SourceString: Spring always gives me this burst of energy. Think it’s the sunshine, {ParentLabel}?
Text.LocalizedString: Spring always gives me this burst of energy. Think it’s the sunshine, {ParentLabel}?

Text.SourceString: This Summer heat is brutal... I’m melting!
Text.LocalizedString: This Summer heat is brutal... I’m melting!

Text.SourceString: I love Summer, but could we dial it down by 10 degrees?
Text.LocalizedString: I love Summer, but could we dial it down by 10 degrees?

Text.SourceString: At least the heat’s worth it for beach days and no school!
Text.LocalizedString: At least the heat’s worth it for beach days and no school!

Text.SourceString: Hey, {ParentLabel}, can we plant some melons this Summer?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, {ParentLabel}, can we plant some melons this Summer?

Text.SourceString: Fall is the best—cool weather, cozy clothes, and the Spooky Festival!
Text.LocalizedString: Fall is the best—cool weather, cozy clothes, and the Spooky Festival!

Text.SourceString: Can we plant pumpkins this year? I really want to carve a few.
Text.LocalizedString: Can we plant pumpkins this year? I really want to carve a few.

Text.SourceString: {SpouseLabel} is pretty awesome...most of the time.
Text.LocalizedString: {SpouseLabel} is pretty awesome...most of the time.

Text.SourceString: {SpouseLabel} said I could stay up late. You’re cool with that, right?
Text.LocalizedString: {SpouseLabel} said I could stay up late. You’re cool with that, right?

Text.SourceString: I’m pretty sure I get my sense of humor from {SpouseLabel}, not you.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m pretty sure I get my sense of humor from {SpouseLabel}, not you.

Text.SourceString: {SpouseLabel} makes the best pancakes, hands down.
Text.LocalizedString: {SpouseLabel} makes the best pancakes, hands down.

Text.SourceString: You always come up with the best ideas, {ParentLabel}.
Text.LocalizedString: You always come up with the best ideas, {ParentLabel}.

Text.SourceString: You’re always so calm, even when things get crazy. I wish I could be more like that.
Text.LocalizedString: You’re always so calm, even when things get crazy. I wish I could be more like that.

Text.SourceString: You’re pretty awesome, {ParentLabel}. I love you and {SpouseLabel}.
Text.LocalizedString: You’re pretty awesome, {ParentLabel}. I love you and {SpouseLabel}.

Text.SourceString: Winter’s fine...if you like freezing all the time. I’m not a fan.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter’s fine...if you like freezing all the time. I’m not a fan.

Text.SourceString: I don't get why people are so into snow. It’s cold and wet!
Text.LocalizedString: I don't get why people are so into snow. It’s cold and wet!

Text.SourceString: Winter would be perfect if it wasn’t so freezing all the time. At least we have the holidays!
Text.LocalizedString: Winter would be perfect if it wasn’t so freezing all the time. At least we have the holidays!

Text.SourceString: Okay, fine, the snow does look kinda nice this year.
Text.LocalizedString: Okay, fine, the snow does look kinda nice this year.

Text.SourceString: It’s freezing out here... Can we get pizza, please?
Text.LocalizedString: It’s freezing out here... Can we get pizza, please?

Text.SourceString: It’s gloomy today, but at least the plants are loving it.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s gloomy today, but at least the plants are loving it.

Text.SourceString: More rain? Great...just what we needed.
Text.LocalizedString: More rain? Great...just what we needed.

Text.SourceString: Hey, at least we don’t need to water the plants today!
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, at least we don’t need to water the plants today!

Text.SourceString: Snow is pretty to look at...but that’s about it.
Text.LocalizedString: Snow is pretty to look at...but that’s about it.

Text.SourceString: Snow again? Time to bundle up like a snowman.
Text.LocalizedString: Snow again? Time to bundle up like a snowman.

Text.SourceString: My face is so cold, I can’t feel it!
Text.LocalizedString: My face is so cold, I can’t feel it!

Text.SourceString: Do we have enough firewood? It's gonna be a cold one tonight.
Text.LocalizedString: Do we have enough firewood? It's gonna be a cold one tonight.

Text.SourceString: Everything’s covered in snow... it’s like a blanket out there.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything’s covered in snow... it’s like a blanket out there.

Text.SourceString: Whoa, look at that snowflake! It’s actually kinda pretty.
Text.LocalizedString: Whoa, look at that snowflake! It’s actually kinda pretty.

Text.SourceString: Did you hear that thunder? That was loud, {ParentLabel}!
Text.LocalizedString: Did you hear that thunder? That was loud, {ParentLabel}!

Text.SourceString: Looks like a storm’s coming in...better stay inside.
Text.LocalizedString: Looks like a storm’s coming in...better stay inside.

Text.SourceString: This storm is intense! Let’s hope the power doesn’t go out!
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is intense! Let’s hope the power doesn’t go out!
